  </ol>


    <p class="organisation__secondary-corporate-information brand--ministry-of-defence">
      Read about the types of information we routinely publish in our <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/publication-scheme">Publication scheme</a>. Find out about our commitment to <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/welsh-language-scheme">publishing in Welsh</a>. Our <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/personal-information-charter">Personal information charter</a> explains how we treat your personal information. Read our policy on <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/social-media-use">Social media use</a>.
    </p>
</div>

    </div>
</div>